WEBVTT

00:13:00.467 --> 00:13:04.094
And so I explained my experience
to her this way:

00:13:04.927 --> 00:13:08.901
that I had sentenced someone to death

00:13:09.761 --> 00:13:12.120
as I served on a jury.

00:13:12.144 --> 00:13:13.561
And I asked her,

00:13:14.479 --> 00:13:16.329
"Did that make me a murderer?"

00:13:17.602 --> 00:13:19.014
She couldn't answer.

00:13:19.645 --> 00:13:24.387
I knew then that this topic
needed to be open for discussion.

00:13:24.411 --> 00:13:25.909
And guess what happened?

00:13:26.574 --> 00:13:29.733
I got invited to speak, just recently,